{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not only us, but there was the county seat, which is Minsk Mazowiecki, which the main governor of the county was there, was all the Jews, and they realized-- they started first, and they told us-- by us, I mean they told the Judenrat in Kaluszyn, we got to work together.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We got to help each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is how we're doing it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we got to buy them in so that they should know that by having something, they've got to give something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this is what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when whenever they came, it was always-- and being friendly to my father, to the Jews, the Poles also became a little softer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, like the Germans working with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were many times, they used to requisite-- they used to take away, you know, the people used to have merchandise, let's say, leather or material they used to bring in from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they  used to come in, they used to take it away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you're not allowed to sell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where did you get it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So by somehow we used to take it back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to take it away and my father used to go there, bring it back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were also taking away-- the farmers used to take their wares to Warsaw, like potatoes or rye or wheat or anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to pass by the place, and they used to take it away from the farmers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being that we had so many people in our town, so many hungry and poor and so on, we used to ask the Germans to give us a wagon of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
